title: Astra Image Photoshop Plug-Ins 5.1.0.0 X64 Cracked
description:
State-of-the-art image processing for incredible photos. Get sharper, clearer images quickly and easily. Deconvolution | Multiscale processing | Denoising | Much more… Awesome Features. Easy to Use.Take a look below at some of the amazing things you can do with Astra Image.

Multiscale Contrast
Adjust the contrast at different scales with separate controls for shadows, midtones and highlights. Make your images really come alive with incredible detail. Our custom edge protection technology means no halos. Brilliant!

Remove Camera Shake
Powerful, configurable tools using the latest algorithms for removing large and small camera shake.

Remove Focus Blur
Use state-of-the-art algorithms to rescue out of focus images and enhance good images. Five blur models are provided, as well as two of the latest deconvolution methods, so you have all the tools you need for refocusing.

Super Contrast
Adjust the shadows, midtones and highlights contrast separately and, at the same time, sharpen the textures and edges.

Denoise
Remove the chrominance and luminance noise from your images using Astra Image. Our state-of-the-art patch-based denoising can take away the noise and leave the details in your images
